node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AlmanacBeer in Almanac Beer Co. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
Need a little Sunshine & Opportunity?⁠
⁠
Try the new Citrus Hibiscus Edition! Brewed with hundreds of pounds of California-grown mandarins, Meyer lemons, limonettes, pomelos, and kumquats. Dried hibiscus flowers finished off the brew, creating this blush-colored beauty!⁠
⁠
Brewmaster @phoederphil says it's "tart like a glass of lemonade and refreshing like a glass of tea. Inspired by pools, porches, and picnics."⁠
⁠
Available at the taproom & on the webstore! All the links are in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AlmanacBeer on August 04, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
PEACH TANGO 🍑💃⁠
⁠
Peach Tango Sour IPA is our newest sour release that will take you on a whirlwind 2-step through a tropical ballroom of tart stonefruit revelry.⁠
⁠
This dry-hopped fox-trot shimmies across your tastebuds with intense notes of ripe peaches and lush Citra & Mosaic hops.⁠
⁠
Pair with shiny shoes, party pants, and your fave boogie-down playlist!🕺 ⁠

node.text:
Time to mask on up friends! 😷⁠
⁠
We've loved seeing your smiling faces at the bar, but it's time to work together to slow the spread of the Delta variant by masking indoors.⁠
⁠
So grab that mask, practice your smize, and we'll see you for a safe pint 🍻

SF FRIENDS! We love seeing you every Saturday 8am-2pm at the Ferry Building Farmers Market! Thanks for always supporting your local brewers and farmers.⁠
⁠
"My weekly visit to the San Francisco Ferry Plaza Farmers Market brings rhythm and meaning to my life."- Alice Waters (Owner, Chez Panisse)⁠
⁠

node.text:
More Nature Gazer IPA is stocked in the taproom & online for your weekend adventures!⁠
⁠
Nature Gazer IPA is an easy-going hazy beer that’s here to remind you to slow down and smell the hops, gaze up at the stars, and enjoy a beer with friends now and again. This liquid daydream has notes of fresh citrus, tropical lychee, and bright grapefruit in every sip.⁠
⁠
Take a moment to admire this awesomely tranquil can art, designed by the beary talented artist Ryan Williams at @asubtledifferencedesign.

node.text:
🌈 SABROSA DIPA 🌈⁠
⁠
Sabrosa DIPA is a mesmerizing flavor adventure. It's a super dank and juicy brew double dry-hopped to the máximo with Sabro and Citra hops. Spellbinding tropical flavors of coconut, tangerine, and ripe cantaloupe permeate the 4th dimension of your tastebuds. Enjoy it with sunshine and magic rainbows!⁠
⁠
Available now at the taproom, on the webstore, and rolling into limited distribution this week!

node.text:
Have you tried Moon Dune?⁠
⁠
Moon Dune was brewed in support of @achievetahoe, a nonprofit focused on providing affordable inclusive outdoor recreation activities that build health, confidence, and independence for people with disabilities.⁠
⁠
This barrel-aged farmhouse ale features fresh Cascade & Centennial hops locally grown in Sonoma County. Enjoy notes of juicy lemon, light farmhouse funk, and just a hint of caramel sweetness.⁠
⁠
AVAILABLE NOW in the taproom and on the webstore!
